{"tid":1535383,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"終結「紅魔噩夢」山神的曼聯真情剖白","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:01:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2154c4e42eac6e405c5e55b97d6c2ec3628617ae","tid":1535383,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"曼聯前鋒阿歷斯山齊士，終於完結「紅魔噩夢」，被借到國際米蘭1季。談起身在曼聯的日子，A山強調沒有後悔加盟，但他不明白為何自己的出場時間這樣少。<br />\n<br />\nA山於2018年1月由阿仙奴轉會曼聯，當時不少球迷、球評家都對他極有期望，認為他可以帶領曼聯挑戰英超冠軍，但最後事與願違。在77場可以落場的賽事中，他僅得31次出任正選；而出場45次僅入5球，毫無疑問這次「紅魔之旅」是失敗的。<br />\n<br />\nA山說：「我依然覺得加盟曼聯是高興的，每次我也這樣說，因為曼聯是英格蘭贏得最多冠軍的球會。我去到阿仙奴時感覺很好，但當時曼聯正在擴軍，他們買好多好球員去爭標。我希望加入並贏得所有錦標，故對轉會曼聯不感後悔。」<br />\n<br />\n「我在曼聯是開心的，但我也會和朋友說希望落場，如果領隊讓我上陣將竭盡所能去爭勝。但我總是踢了60分鐘就被換走，之後下一仗就失去上陣機會，對此我真的不明白。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=5e9cc03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"bee147aa95d63272d2fe21fd0e138b3aa485c1cd","tid":1535383,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb6fb0af3bf6e226dcaee3c510a56c9fe2978e16","tid":1535383,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"山神曼聯highlight<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/opeX17I7N-M/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FopeX17I7N-M%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=1618c780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2018/01/23/13/4877FA8700000578-0-image-m-33_1516714330114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F13%2F4877FA8700000578-0-image-m-33_1516714330114.jpg&h=98347ca5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f07c9c05f3b822d97cb008c4b431e108b7dc151d","tid":1535383,"uid":317058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"原本佢加盟嗰陣我都好開心<br />\n點知仲廢過楊格"},{"pid":"e844524682fda2dc3aa24880268ae05771b86d57","tid":1535383,"uid":9150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"45場入得5球，<br />\n當年雲佩斯加盟38場入左26球<br />\n點解？"}]}